{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>What Is It?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Spiritus Vindicta is a fun addition to the ever expanding ghost hunting genre bringing a new 2D, single-player experience to the table. Follow along a simple story as you take up the task of finding, and exorcising, the ghost that changed everything. Throughout your journey, you'll head out on numerous missions to haunted locations as you investigate the ghosts lurking there. You will need to find and log evidence as you explore each location in order to learn about the ghosts and what you need to do to exorcise them. Experience what it's like to search in fear as you fight to stay calm and, most importantly, alive. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>What to Expect</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">For those who are familiar with the ghost hunting genre, you'll probably feel right at home with exploring environments for evidence while trying to survive ghost hunts. However, you'll notice a few differences as this game aims to be less realistic and slightly faster paced. There will still be a few scares along the way, but a more traditional game-like tone underlies the experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Investigate and exorcise 10 different types of ghosts</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience different ghost attacks as they get more dangerous over the course of the story.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162260/extras/example_attack_01.gif?t=1729503254\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Be ready to hide from ghosts on the hunt</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162260/extras/example_hunt_01.gif?t=1729503254\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Explore mo